Package io.github.ai4ci.output

Interface OutbreakCSV

All Superinterfaces:
CommonCSV.Execution, CommonCSV.Model, CommonCSV.State, OutputWriter.Writeable
@Immutable public interface OutbreakCSV extends CommonCSV.State
Per‑state outbreak summary exported during simulation updates.

Main purpose: provide a compact per‑time summary of outbreak metrics such as incidence, prevalence and averages. Records are produced at the UPDATE stage and are written per simulation state (one row per time step) to a CSV file (summary.csv).

Downstream uses: used for plotting time series, quick diagnostics and as an input to aggregate analyses across replications.

Author:
Rob Challen
